# APIs layer

- `lib/apis/clients/` — Retrofit service interfaces
- `lib/apis/interceptors/` — Dio interceptors (auth token, logging)
- `lib/apis/common/`, `lib/apis/core/` — shared API utilities

## Rules

- No UI in `lib/apis/`.
- Register new services via `@injectable` modules; run `build_runner` after changes.
- Coordinate router/DI changes with `integration-wiring` subagent when adding endpoints for a new epic.
